will pay a rent of Pounds 19.50 per sq ft.
The Department of the Environment, which shares Marsham Street with the
transport department, has already announced plans to move to Eland House,
which will be built close to Victoria station. The Marsham Street building
will be demolished after the two government departments have moved.
