</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
Howard Evans, a partner at accountants Price Waterhouse, has been appointed
finance director of chemicals company Courtaulds. He has had 10 years'
involvement with Courtaulds at PW and has been in charge of the group's
audit for the past year.
Evans replaces Michael Pragnell, who becomes director responsible for
Courtaulds' new polymer products division. He spent less than two years in
